    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200\u00b0C/ 180\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice<strong> half </strong>your <strong>red onion[s] </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Roughly chop half<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veggie-cheeseburger-rice-bake-with-saucy-relish/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>meat-free patty[ies]</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Once browned, add the<strong> sliced onion</strong>, <strong>chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for a further 3-4 min or until the onion has softened \u2013 this is your <strong>spiced meat-free mixture</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veggie-cheeseburger-rice-bake-with-saucy-relish/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>spiced meat-free mixture</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>white long grain rice </strong>and 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[525ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[700ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cover tightly with<strong> tin foil</strong>, and put the dish in the oven for 30 min or until all the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veggie-cheeseburger-rice-bake-with-saucy-relish/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dice your <strong>cucumber<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>finely</p><p>Dice the <strong>remaining onion </strong>finely</p><p>Add the <strong>diced cucumber</strong> and <strong>diced onion</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside \u2013 this is your <strong>quick-pickled onion & cucumber</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veggie-cheeseburger-rice-bake-with-saucy-relish/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Dice the<strong> remaining tomato</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mustard ketchup</strong>, <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>ketchup</strong> in a bowl \u2013 this is your <strong>sauce</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veggie-cheeseburger-rice-bake-with-saucy-relish/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, remove the dish from the oven and discard the foil</p><p>Top the<strong> cooked rice </strong>with the<strong> grated cheese </strong>and return it to the oven for a further 5 min or until the cheese has melted \u2013 this is your <strong>veggie 'cheeseburger' rice bake</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veggie-cheeseburger-rice-bake-with-saucy-relish/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add 1/2 tsp per person <strong>pickling liquid</strong> from the quick pickled onion & cucumber<strong> </strong>to the <strong>sauce</strong>,<strong> </strong>discard the remaining liquid</p><p>Mix everything together \u2013 this is your <strong>burger sauce</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>diced tomato</strong> with the <strong>drained quick pickled onion & cucumber </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>tomato relish</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veggie-cheeseburger-rice-bake-with-saucy-relish/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>veggie 'cheeseburger' rice bake</strong> with some of the <strong>burger sauce</strong> drizzled all over</p><p>Top with some the<strong> tomato relish</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining burger sauce</strong> with any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>tomato relish</strong> and serve to the side \u2013 this is your <strong>saucy relish</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
